ZH: 我们鼓励员工自觉自愿地参加公司的培训计划。
EN: We encourage employees to voluntarily participate in the company's training programs.

ZH: 作为一名市民，你应该自觉自愿地遵守交通规则。
EN: As a citizen, you should willingly abide by traffic rules.

ZH: 志愿者们自觉自愿地为社区服务，为他人带来帮助。
EN: Volunteers willingly serve the community and help others.

ZH: 我们希望每个学生都可以自觉自愿地参加学校的义工活动。
EN: We hope every student can voluntarily participate in the school's volunteer activities.

ZH: 雇主不能强迫员工自觉自愿地加班。
EN: Employers cannot force employees to voluntarily work overtime.

ZH: 他们自觉自愿地加入了环保组织，为保护环境出力。
EN: They voluntarily joined the environmental organization and worked hard to protect the environment.

ZH: 每个人都有自愿学习的权利和义务。
EN: Everyone has the right and obligation to voluntarily learn.

ZH: 孩子们应该自觉自愿地遵守学校的规章制度。
EN: Children should voluntarily abide by the school rules.

ZH: 公民在捐献血液时是自觉自愿的，不能被强迫。
EN: Citizens donating blood do so voluntarily and cannot be forced.

ZH: 在这个活动中，参与者是自觉自愿地提供服务的。
EN: In this event, participants voluntarily provide services.

ZH: 社会公众应该自觉自愿地支持公益事业。
EN: The public should willingly support charitable causes.

ZH: 我们鼓励志愿者们自觉自愿地投入到灾区救援工作中。
EN: We encourage volunteers to voluntarily participate in disaster relief efforts.

ZH: 作为一名老师，我们应该自觉自愿地提供帮助和指导给学生。
EN: As a teacher, we should willingly offer help and guidance to students.

ZH: 志愿者们自觉自愿地参与了社区清洁活动。
EN: Volunteers voluntarily participated in the community clean-up activity.

ZH: 学生需自觉自愿地遵守学校的学习纪律。
EN: Students need to voluntarily abide by the school's academic discipline.

ZH: 我们强调自觉自愿地参加这次活动，不能被强迫。
EN: We emphasize voluntary participation in this event and cannot be forced.

ZH: 公民有权利自愿捐款支持慈善机构。
EN: Citizens have the right to voluntarily donate money to support charitable organizations.

ZH: 家长们应该鼓励孩子们自觉自愿地参加社区服务活动。
EN: Parents should encourage children to voluntarily participate in community service activities.

ZH: 志愿者们自觉自愿地为灾区捐赠食物和物资。
EN: Volunteers voluntarily donated food and supplies to disaster areas.

ZH: 我们希望每个人都能自觉自愿地为环保事业贡献力量。
EN: We hope everyone can willingly contribute to environmental conservation efforts.
